  "title": "Isolated Point",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $X\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ and let $x\\in X$. The point $x$ is an\n\\textbf{isolated point} of $X$ if\n\\[\n \\exists\\varepsilon>0\\;\\bigl(V_\\varepsilon(x)\\cap X=\\{x\\}\\bigr).\n\\]",
